00:00:17.010 --> 00:00:24.820
They were 12 of them

00:00:24.820 --> 00:00:28.820
They were there when Jesus healed the sick

00:00:28.820 --> 00:00:35.729
The blind buds, let's try to remember

00:00:35.729 --> 00:01:46.120
There was Andrew John
